synthesis_method: The electrolyte synthesis process involved mixing LiCl, YCl3, and ZrCl4 in a molar ratio of 2.9:0.9:0.1, pulverizing and mixing the powders, and subjecting them to a 25-hour milling treatment at 600rpm using a planetary ball mill to obtain a powder of the solid electrolyte material Li2.9Y0.9Zr0.1Cl6.
